   <tbody> 
    <tr> 
     <th style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"> <h2>Black Blade</h2> </th> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"><img style="width: 200px; height: 200px;" title="black_blade_spell_item_elden_ring_wiki_guide_200px" src="/file/Elden-Ring/black_blade_incantation_elden_ring_wiki_guide_200px.png" alt="black blade incantation elden ring wiki guide 200px" width="200" height="200"></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td>Spell Type</td> 
     <td><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Erdtree Incantations" href="/Erdtree+Incantations" target="">Erdtree Incantations</a></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td>FP Cost&nbsp;26</td> 
     <td>Slots Used&nbsp;2</td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td colspan="2"><img title="item_effect_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_18px" src="/file/Elden-Ring/item_effects_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_55px_18px.png" alt="item effects icon elden ring wiki guide 55px 18px" width="18" height="18">Effect 
      <div class="lineleft">
        Black blade spinning slash that emits wave of light. 
      </div> <br><img style="float: left;" title="Attributes Requirement" src="/file/Elden-Ring/attributes-required-elden-ring-wiki-guide-18.png" alt="attributes required elden ring wiki guide 18" width="18" height="18">Requires 
      <div class="lineleft"> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Intelligence" href="/Intelligence" target="">Intelligence</a> 0 
       <br> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Faith" href="/Faith" target="">Faith</a>&nbsp;46 
       <br> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Arcane" href="/Arcane" target="">Arcane</a>&nbsp;0 
      </div> </td> 
    </tr> 
   </tbody> 
  </table> 
 </div> 
</div> 
<p><strong>Black Blade</strong> is an <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Incantations" href="/Incantations" target="">Incantation</a> in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Wiki" href="/Elden+Ring+Wiki">Elden Ring</a>. <strong>Black Blade spell</strong>&nbsp;throws a drill attack emitting a wave of light.&nbsp;Updated to&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Patch Notes" href="/Patch+Notes">Patch 1.07</a>.</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<div class="lineleft"> 
 <p><em>Power gleaned from the remembrance of Maliketh.</em></p> 
 <p><em>Caster creates an illusory black blade, then leaps forward to&nbsp;</em><em>deliver a spinning slash that emits a wave of light.&nbsp;</em><em>This can be followed up with one additional attack.</em></p> 
 <p><em>This blade was once imbued with Destined Death. In addition to&nbsp;</em><em>dealing damage, it reduces foes' maximum HP and continues to&nbsp;</em><em>sap their current HP for a very short time.</em></p> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Where to find Black Blade</h3> 
<p>Where to find <strong>Black Blade</strong>:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>Trade <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Remembrance of the Black Blade" href="/Remembrance+of+the+Black+Blade" target="">Remembrance of the Black Blade</a>&nbsp;with&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Enia" href="/Enia">Enia</a>&nbsp;at&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Roundtable Hold" href="/Roundtable+Hold">Roundtable Hold</a>.</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Elden Ring&nbsp;Black Blade Guide</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Erdtree Incantations" href="/Erdtree+Incantations" target="">Erdtree Incantation</a></li> 
 <li>Stamina Cost:&nbsp;44</li> 
 <li><span style="color: #ff9900;">Note:</span>&nbsp;In&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Patch Notes" href="/Patch+Notes">Patch 1.07</a>, the stamina cost has been reduced to 44 from 51.&nbsp;Improved turning performance and shortened recovery time.&nbsp;The sword and the wave attack have been changed so that they hit at the same time.&nbsp;Attack power, stamina attack power and poise damage of each part have been decreased.&nbsp;Decreased the number of times the wave part hits large enemies.<br>(This incantation&nbsp;is currently missing its follow up attack when cast from the left hand. This issue will be corrected in a future update.)</li> 
 <li>Reduces enemy max HP by 10% for 15 seconds.</li> 
 <li>Saps enemy HP for 2 seconds</li> 
 <li>The damage type is 100%&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Holy Damage" href="/Holy+Damage">Holy Damage</a>. The sapping damage can be increased by&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Holy-Shrouding Cracked Tear" href="/Holy-Shrouding+Cracked+Tear">Holy-Shrouding Cracked Tear</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Sacred Scorpion Charm" href="/Sacred+Scorpion+Charm">Sacred Scorpion Charm</a>, as well as other generic attack buffs like&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Golden Vow" href="/Golden+Vow">Golden Vow</a>, etc.</li> 
 <li>Debuff stacks with either the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Destined Death" href="/Destined+Death" target="">Destined Death</a>&nbsp;<strong>OR</strong>&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Blade of Death" href="/Blade+of+Death" target="">Blade of Death</a>&nbsp;but&nbsp;<strong>NOT</strong>&nbsp;both.</li> 
 <li>Black Blade performs a spinning slash that emits a vertical wave that passes through enemies. The follow-up spin and its wave is angled diagonally. 
  <ul> 
   <li>See&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Buffs and Debuffs" href="/Buffs+and+Debuffs" target="">Buffs and Debuffs</a>&nbsp;for more information on stacking debuffs.</li> 
  </ul> </li> 
</ul> 
<ul> 
 <li><img title="Black Blade Gif" src="/file/Elden-Ring/ezgif-4-4a26cf6448.gif" alt="ezgif 4 4a26cf6448" width="600" height="338"></li> 
</ul> 
